== 背景 ==
自民黨總裁選舉原定2021年9月举行，但由於時任自民黨总裁、日本首相[[安倍晋三|安倍晋三]]于2020年8月28日突然以健康问题为由辞职<ref name="AbeResignsBBC">{{Cite web|title=Shinzo Abe: Japan's PM resigns for health reasons|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-53943758|accessdate=28 August 2020|date=28 August 2020|work=BBC News|archive-date=2020-08-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200828080617/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-53943758|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="AbeResignsAljazeera">{{Cite web|title=Japan's PM Shinzo Abe resigns because of ill-health|url=https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2020/08/japan-abe-meet-media-hospital-visits-fuel-health-concerns-200828001333144.html|accessdate=28 August 2020|date=28 August 2020|work=[[半岛电视台|半岛电视台]]|archive-date=2020-08-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200828022653/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2020/08/japan-abe-meet-media-hospital-visits-fuel-health-concerns-200828001333144.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="AbeResignsNationalPost">{{Cite web|title=Japan's Shinzo Abe steps down as PM due to health concerns|url=https://nationalpost.com/news/world/japans-shinzo-abe-steps-down-as-pm-amid-health-concerns|accessdate=28 August 2020|date=28 August 2020|work=National Post|archive-date=2020-09-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200914124909/https://nationalpost.com/news/world/japans-shinzo-abe-steps-down-as-pm-amid-health-concerns|dead-url=no}}</ref>，迫使自民黨總裁選舉提前1年舉行。由于自民党控制着日本国会的多数席位，自民黨總裁選舉獲胜者将毫無懸念接替安倍晉三出任日本首相，完成安倍首相的剩餘任期<ref>{{Cite news|author=Landers|first=Peter|author2=Gale|first2=Alastair|title=Shinzo Abe Will Resign as Japan’s Prime Minister, Citing His Health|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/shinzo-abe-to-resign-as-japanese-pm-due-to-health-concerns-local-media-says-11598592532|accessdate=30 August 2020|work=Wall Street Journal|date=29 August 2020|archive-date=2020-08-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200829171939/https://www.wsj.com/articles/shinzo-abe-to-resign-as-japanese-pm-due-to-health-concerns-local-media-says-11598592532|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

自民黨總務會在2020年9月1日召開會議，決定以簡易型方式，即不辦黨員投票，是2008年自民黨總裁選舉後首次。這意味總裁選舉將計算國會議員票394票，與47個都道府縣各3票共141張的地方票，合計535票選出總裁<ref name="a2">{{cite news |title=日本自民黨總裁選舉不辦黨員投票 有利菅義偉出線 |url=https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202009010131.aspx |accessdate=2021-09-26 |agency=Central News Agency |date=2020-09-01 |archive-date=2021-09-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210926190940/https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202009010131.aspx }}</ref>。

